relics.name: Dreambreaker
relics.flavorText: Hailing from a mystical dreamworld, and the bringer of its end.

relics.name: Wooden Stool
relics.description: At the end of combat, if your HP is lower than at the start of combat, restore up to 5 missing HP.
relics.flavorText: The Dreamwalker never lets an opportunity go to waste to rest on one of these.

relics.name: Empathy
relics.description: Whenever an enemy dies, heal 3 HP. Max 3 times per combat.
relics.flavorText: One of many aspects gained by the Dreamwalker on her journey.

relics.name: Detached Blade
relics.description: Draw 1 card for every 5th sybilmod:MP you gain.
relics.flavorText: This large blade once hung off the princess' long braid, serving as her weapon.

relics.name: Silver Key
relics.description: Gain 1 additional sybilmod:MP for every 3rd MP you gain.
relics.flavorText: These small keys usually opened doors to optional rewards for the Dreamwalker.

relics.name: Sol Censer
relics.description: At the start of your turn, cleanse all Weak and Frail on you. Consume sybilmod:Magical_Power equal to the number of cleansed stacks times 2.
relics.flavorText: Rejuvenation through the power of the sun.

relics.name: Sol Chain
relics.description: At the start of combat, if your HP is lower than at the start of last combat, gain the difference as sybilmod:Magical_Power.
relics.flavorText: Imbued with the power of the sun.

relics.name: Fake Horns
relics.description: Draw 1 more card whenever you're drawing cards beyond the start of your turn.
relics.flavorText: The Dreamwalker wore these as part of a disguise to infiltrate the princess' realm.

relics.name: Golden Key
relics.description: Gain 1 [E] for every 5th sybilmod:MP you gain.
relics.flavorText: The Dreamwalker gathered 5 of these during her journey through the princess' realm.

relics.name: Solbreaker
relics.description: Replaces Dreambreaker. Gain 1 additional sybilmod:Magical_Power on attacks. At the start of your turn, lower your MP to 30 if it exceeds that value.
relics.flavorText: The Dreambreaker, infused with the power of the sun.

relics.name: Dream Mirror
relics.description: At the start of combat, gain all sybilmod:MP you've consumed last combat (max: 10.)
relics.flavorText: The portal from which the Dreamwalker entered the princess' realm.

relics.name: Sol Shield
relics.description: Whenever you gain sybilmod:MP, gain that much Block.
relics.flavorText: A protective aura formed by converting any excess energy unleashed by the power of the sun.

keywords.name: This is displayed in the tooltip.
keywords.description: This is displayed in the tooltip. Spaces should not be used be avoided in NAMES, with the exception of multi-word keywords (see next entry).

keywords.name: Magical Damage
keywords.description: Non-physical damage which bypasses effects like Thorns. Does not stack with damage boosts.

keywords.name: Magical Power
keywords.description: Gained by attacking. Every fourth MP adds 1 bonus damage. Unlock unique buffs by reaching 16 and 30 MP.

keywords.name: Multiword Keyword
keywords.description: Make sure the first element in NAMES has no underscores. The rest should use _ in the place of spaces. In card text, you'll use the underscore versions.

mods.description: Slay the Spire as Sybil from Pseudoregalia!
